Package: ziln
Type: Package
Title: Zero inflated log-normal model for inference of sparse association networks
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Margaret", "Janiczek", email = "mjaniczek@umass.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements the code provided from Prost V, Gazut S, Bruls T (2021) 
    A zero inflated log-normal model for inference of sparse microbial association networks. 
    PLoS Comput Biol 17(6): e1009089
    Turns code provided with that paper into a package useful for implementing their 
    method into an analysis pipeline. 
